Dividend Policy
We have never paid and do not expect to pay dividends on our common stock for the foreseeable future. The declaration and
payment of dividends is subject to the discretion of our board of directors and depends on various factors, including our net income,
financial condition, cash requirements, future prospects, and other factors considered relevant by our board of directors. We expect
to prioritize our working capital requirements, capacity expansion and other capital expenditure needs, R&D and technology
investments, and merger and acquisition opportunities prior to returning capital to our shareholders.
