Gross profit may be affected by numerous factors, including the selling prices of our modules and the selling prices of projects and
services included in our residual business operations, our manufacturing costs, the capacity utilization of our manufacturing
facilities, and foreign exchange rates. Gross profit may also be affected by the mix of net sales from our modules business and
residual business operations.
